item.title: Kai and Mika tonight
item.description: 00:42 Saturday 25 November 2017 JST Hung out with Kai and Mika near Mika’s work tonight. They gave me a stack of flyers to hand out for a show that Mika and Kai will be staffing on Monday. Thanks to Mika for sending my medium rare burger back to be recooked to well done as I had ordered! Thanks to Mama for snacks she brought back today from her trip.
